text: Leninsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Austrumsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 43 km from Iglino, 7 km from Austrum. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Leninsky, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
